{
  "chapter": 38,
  "chapter_summary": "小鱼儿在酒楼赴宴后遭玉面神判萧子春、金狮李迪等人围杀，危急时刻嗜赌如命的恶赌鬼轩辕三光从天而降，一口酒击退鬼影子何无双，以绝顶武功震慑全场。轩辕三光逼江玉郎赌手臂，江南大侠江别鹤及时赶到。江别鹤以巧计设下鱼翅羹赌局，用精湛掌力将碗中鱼翅一滴不溅地击穿桌面，令轩辕三光自愧不如当场认输。江别鹤仅罚轩辕三光一杯酒，展现出胸襟气度，赢得众人敬服。小鱼儿被江别鹤带回，与江玉郎同住。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "肚兄肚兄，今日我总算对得起你了吧！",
      "tone": "嬉笑",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_pan",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神判",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "酒菜都已够了么？可要再用些瓜果？",
      "tone": "客气",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_pan",
      "text": "我很想，只是肚子却不答应。",
      "tone": "诙谐",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_pan",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神判",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "既是如此，我等总算不负神锡道长之托，已尽过地主之谊了。",
      "tone": "客套",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_pan",
      "text": "你话里好像有话……",
      "tone": "警觉",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_pan",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神判",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "阁下不妨先推开窗子看看。",
      "tone": "阴沉",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_pan",
      "text": "这算什么？",
      "tone": "不以为意",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_pan",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神判",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "受人之托，忠人之事，神锡道长托我好生招待于你，我等便尽了地主之谊。但还有一人，却托我等来取你的头颅，你看怎样？",
      "tone": "冷冷",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_pan",
      "text": "我这颗脑袋居然还有人要，这倒真是荣幸之至，但要我脑袋的这人又是准？你总该说来听听。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_pan",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神判",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你只需知道他有一个鼻子两只眼睛已足够了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来，今天我只得将脑袋送给你们了……一盆蜜汁火腿就换去了我的脑袋，这岂非太便宜了些！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_shi_li_di",
      "speaker_name": "李迪",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你还要我等动手么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jin_shi_li_di",
      "text": "用不着了，只是不知道你的刀快不快？若是一刀保险可以切下脑袋，我倒想借来用用。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_shi_li_di",
      "speaker_name": "李迪",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "好，念你死到临头，还有谈笑的本事，某家就把这柄刀借给你。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_pan",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神判",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你为何不拔？你拔出这柄刀来，就可以一刀砍向我，或是别的人，或是将刀架在江玉郎的脖子上，逼我们放走你。",
      "tone": "冷冷",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_pan",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神判",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你不敢拔这柄刀的，是吗？只因为你自己也知道，只要你拔出这柄刀，只有死得更惨。",
      "tone": "阴沉",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_pan",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神判",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "念你是个聪明人，且给你个速死，咄，去吧！",
      "tone": "叱",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_pan",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神判",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么人？",
      "tone": "厉喝",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_pan",
      "text": "谁是你的兄台，你是什么玩意儿？",
      "tone": "冷冷",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_pan",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神判",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "在下萧子春，江湖人称玉面神判。",
      "tone": "勉强忍怒",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_pan",
      "text": "好个响亮的名头，你配么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_shi_li_di",
      "speaker_name": "李迪",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你……你便是恶赌鬼轩辕三光！",
      "tone": "失声",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "儿子们眼见老子来了，怎地还不快摆上酒菜！",
      "tone": "冷冷",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_shi_li_di",
      "speaker_name": "李迪",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "小二，瞧见老子来了，为何还不摆上菜来。",
      "tone": "大喝",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁要你斟酒？除了对面两个姓江的娃儿，全给老子远远站开。",
      "tone": "瞪眼",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "喝！",
      "tone": "命令",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "怎么？你不赌？",
      "tone": "瞪眼",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "吐……吐……吐……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "好，你龟儿子要赌啥？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "吐……吐什么……都可以。",
      "tone": "颤抖",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "好，老子就赌你这条手臂。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "轩辕先生若要赌，在下可以奉陪，寻这等黄口孺子来赌，岂非无趣么？",
      "tone": "朗声笑",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "动容",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "在下江别鹤。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "江湖传言，江南一带，出了个了不起的英雄，乃是燕南天之后第一个当得起大侠两字的人物，莫非就是你？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "那只是江湖朋友抬爱，在下怎担当得起。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "虎父犬子……虎父犬子……",
      "tone": "摇头叹",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "他既是你儿子，你莫非要代他与我赌一赌？",
      "tone": "大喝",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "轩辕先生若有兴致，在下自当奉陪。不知轩辕先生赌注如何？",
      "tone": "平和",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "你我俩人无论谁输了，便任凭对方处置！",
      "tone": "大声",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "就是这样也好，但如何赌法，还请见告。",
      "tone": "淡淡",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "好，江南大侠果然豪气干云，我定了赌注，如何赌法便由得你，这是我的规矩。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "既是如此，在下恭敬不如从命了。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "这又算什么？",
      "tone": "奇怪",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你我依次往桌上击一掌，谁若将这碗鱼翅震得溅出，或是使得碗落下去，那人便算输了。",
      "tone": "缓缓",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你我一掌击下，必定穿透桌面，是以就算你我俩人都未将这碗鱼翅羹震倒，到了后来，桌面上俱是掌痕，那中央一块，总要落下去的，谁击下最后一掌，谁就输了，是以桌子越小，胜负便越早。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "这样的赌法，倒真连我也未曾见过。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "在下已击下了第一掌，此刻该轮到轩辕先生了。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "我恶赌鬼平生与人大赌小赌，不下万次，从未有一次还未赌时，便已先认输了……但这次，我不必赌，已认输了……我掌力纵能穿透桌面，却万万不能令这碗见鬼的鱼翅羹一滴也不溅出来。",
      "tone": "狂笑转惨然",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "现在，你要我怎样，只管说吧！",
      "tone": "惨然",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "现在轩辕三光是生是死，往东往西，但凭阁下吩咐！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 38
    }
  ],
